'''异烟酸'''（'''吡啶-4-甲酸'''）是一种[[有机化合物|有机化合物]]，化学式为C<sub>5</sub>H<sub>4</sub>N(CO<sub>2</sub>H)，是[[吡啶甲酸|吡啶甲酸]]的[[同分异构体|同分异构体]]之一。它可由[[:d:Q23636732|吡啶-4-甲醛]]<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Synthesis|volume=1993|issue=03|language=en|issn=0039-7881|date=1993|pages=295–297|doi=10.1055/s-1993-25851|url=http://www.thieme-connect.de/DOI/DOI?10.1055/s-1993-25851|title=The Oxidation of Aromatic Aldehydes to Carboxylic Acids Using Hydrogen Peroxide in Formic Acid|accessdate=2020-09-20|author=Robert H. Dodd, Mireille Le Hyaric|archive-date=2018-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180605181641/https://www.thieme-connect.de/DOI/DOI?10.1055%2Fs-1993-25851}}</ref>、[[:d:Q27464630|吡啶-4-甲醇]]<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Green Chemistry|volume=19|issue=23|language=en|issn=1463-9262|date=2017|pages=5548–5552|doi=10.1039/C7GC02802D|url=http://xlink.rsc.org/?DOI=C7GC02802D|title=Iodine catalyzed oxidation of alcohols and aldehydes to carboxylic acids in water: a metal-free route to the synthesis of furandicarboxylic acid and terephthalic acid|accessdate=2020-09-20|author=Susanta Hazra, Mayukh Deb, Anil J. Elias}}</ref>或[[4-甲基吡啶|4-甲基吡啶]]<ref>Parker, Kathlyn A.; Ledeboer, Mark W.; Pettigrew, Jeremy D. Nitric acid. ''e-EROS Encyclopedia of Reagents for Organic Synthesis'', 2009. pp 1-7. ISBN 978-0-470-84289-8.</ref>的氧化反应制得。它和[[氯化亚砜|氯化亚砜]]反应，可以得到吡啶-4-甲酰氯。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Asian Journal of Chemistry|volume=26|issue=1|date=2014|pages=209–215|doi=10.14233/ajchem.2014.15572|url=http://www.asianjournalofchemistry.co.in/User/ViewFreeArticle.aspx?ArticleID=26_2_48|title=Design, Synthesis and Antibacterial Evaluation of Novel Fluoroquinolone and its Derivatives|accessdate=2020-09-20|author=Kang-Min Wang, Yuan-Cheng Qin, Guan-Jun Cheng, Hua-Jun Zhu, Long Liang, Zhi-Peng Cheng, Mei-Ming Luo|archive-date=2022-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220225102135/https://asianjournalofchemistry.co.in/User/ViewFreeArticle.aspx?ArticleID=26_2_48}}</ref>

